Walsall FC boss on Bielik: &quot;I know that Krystian has got a slight niggle, we knew that. Whether he is right for the weekend, I&rsquo;m unsure. But I&rsquo;m not going to risk him as we need him for the remainder of the season.&quot;<br />
<br />
Walsall boss on Bielik: &ldquo;Krystian has had a setback in his rehab. He has tweaked his knee during late-stage rehab which has delayed the start of his loan spell with us. Krystian is due at the club in the next 10 days to meet with the squad and take part in some group sessions.&rdquo;
